name: tripla personalidade sem variedade
description:
triple personality without variation

-

This piece is from the collection "descartável", which is a audiovisual project that I discarded bad feelings and turned it into something that could heal me. The project addresses mental health issues, self knowledge and it was a opportunity to me to study animation. This is the 26th piece of the collection.

See more at: https://qabri.eu
